---
// Hero component with CTA
---
<section class="relative bg-white py-16 px-6 lg:px-20 lg:flex items-center justify-between min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden">
  <img 
      src="/src/image/component1.png" 
      alt="" 
      class="absolute top-[10%] left-15 -translate-y-1/2 w-[3%] max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-90"
    />
  <div class="lg:w-1/2 space-y-8 z-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-normal text-[#003366] leading-tight font-montserrat">
      Atención Médica Integral y <br/>
      <span class="text-[#0056b3] font-black">Ambulancias UCI 24/7</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg max-w-md font-montserrat">
      Soporte avanzado y ambulancias UCI las 24 horas. Conexión inmediata entre El Vigía, San Cristóbal y Mérida.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="#" class="bg-[#0056b3] inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 font-montserrat">
        Llamar Emergencia
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-3">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
          <path d="M15 2h6v6"></path>
          <path d="M15 8l6-6"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="border-2 border-black text-black px-10 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all font-montserrat">
        Afíliate Ahora
      </a>
    </div>
   
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative lg:w-1/2 mt-12 lg:mt-0 flex justify-center items-center">
    <img 
      src="/src/image/elipsi.png" 
      alt="" 
      class="absolute right-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[100%] max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-90"
    />
    
    <img 
      src="/src/image/hero.png" 
      alt="Personal Sima24" 
      class="relative z-10 w-[100%] right-[-10%] max-w-[550px] drop-shadow-2xl" 
    />
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 text-blue-600 text-4xl font-bold z-20 animate-pulse">+</div>
  </div>
 <img 
      src="/src/image/component2.png" 
      alt="" 
      class="absolute bottom-[6%] left-[45%] -translate-y-1/2 w-[3%] max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-90"
    />
   <img 
      src="/src/image/ellipse bajo.png" 
      alt="" 
      class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-0 -translate-y-1/2 w-[110%] max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-90"
    />
</section>